@node Beschreibung "Description of the program"

GurpsGen is an utility, which can GMs use to create NPC. it contains
the rules written down in the basicbook, page 84/85.
Equipment must be added manually. the character can be used in
all periods.

the program is GIFTWARE, it means, if you think, it's good, you can
send me something, postcards, emails, money, computers, ...

the program is startet in the CLI with following parameters
 GurpsGen -a <MinAttrib> -s <MinSumAttrib> -l <language>
    MinAttrib    : minimum of each attributes (ST,DX,HT,IQ).
                   default : 12
    MinSumAttrib : minimal sum of attributes (ST,DX,HT,IQ).
                   default : 3
    language     : 1 - german (default)
                   2 - english

